\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Switch abierto circuito simplificado
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $V_{OUT}=I_{LKG}\cdot R_{LOAD}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
En cuanto a la transferencia, para alterna, se tiene el siguiente esquema
 a llave cerrada:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
placement H
wide false
sideways false
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\align center
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename Screenshot 2019-04-04 14.50.43.png

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Circuito AC a llave cerrada
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Y desarrollando se llega a:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $A_{dB}=20\cdot log[\frac{R_{LOAD}}{R_{LOAD}+R_{ON}}]+10\cdot log[\omega^{2}\cdot(R_{ON}\cdot C_{DS})^{2}+1]-10\cdot log[\omega^{2}\cdot((\frac{R_{LOAD}\cdot R_{ON}}{R_{LOAD}+R_{ON}})^{2}\cdot((C_{LOAD}+C_{D}+C_{DS})^{2}+1)]$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
La cual corresponde a un pasa bajos de los siguientes parámetros:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $f_{zero}=\frac{0.159}{R_{ON}\cdot C_{DS}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $f_{pole}=\frac{0.159}{(R_{LOAD}//R_{ON})\cdot(C_{LOAD}+C_{D}+C_{DS})}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $A(0)$
\end_inset

=
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{R_{LOAD}}{R_{LOAD}+R_{ON}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A llave abierta se tiene el siguiente esquema:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
placement H
wide false
sideways false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\align center
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename Screenshot 2019-04-04 15.14.18.png
	scale 80

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Circuito AC a llave abierta
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
El cual planteando la función transferencia se llega a:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $A(s)=\frac{s\cdot R_{LOAD}\cdot C_{DS}}{s\cdot R_{LOAD}\cdot(C_{LOAD}+C_{D}+C_{DS})+1}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
El cual corresponde a un pasa altos con los siguientes parámetros:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $f_{zero}=\frac{0.159}{R_{LOAD}\cdot(C_{LOAD}+C_{D}+C_{DS})}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align center
\begin_inset Formula $A(0)=0$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Elección de llave analógica
